name: The Collector
description:
Collaboration with NFT artist and Collector, Inlecebra. Inspired by the relationship between artist and collector in the NFT world. A world that has sparked connection and bond between the two that enables forward movement as a team.

Body painted with UV Blacklight paint for that special neon synth feel to represent the digital art era. The flowers represent the NFTs (OBJKTs) that the collector collects.
